{"tid":1795056,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國工會拒「聖誕休戰」 料全國工業行動持續","createTime":"2019-12-23T14:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T15:40:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd850572f7c50b604442ebbc8044ec965bece57","tid":1795056,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"聖誕節在即，法國反對退休金改革引發的大罷工未見平息，工會拒絕聖誕休戰，料全國在聖誕節期間將繼續有工業行動，交通混亂情況亦持續。<br />\n<br />\n盡管總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）宣布放棄卸任後酬勞以示釋出善意，但行動跟示威者針對的退休金改革無關，無助平息眾怒，工會決定繼續在聖誕期間繼續工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n鐵路方面，國家鐵路局（SNCF）已經定出未來數日的服務時間表，顯示鐵路僅可維持有限度服務。TGC高鐵提供的班次約為正常的40%，廉價的Ouigo則只得一半服務。<br />\n<br />\n在巴黎，雖然只得兩條地鐵線路維持全日服務，但已較周日為佳，分別為1號線和14號線，均屬自動駕駛。另有6條線全日關閉。<br />\n<br />\n航空交通方面，暫未有航班被迫取消，但法國南部遇上暴風雨，有航班因而受影響。<br />\n<br />\n強硬派工會CGT的罷工，更導致里昂（Lyon）和波爾多（Bordeaux）等地停電，影響數以萬戶，甚至周末兩場欖球賽也因為球場停電而中斷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2526283/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2526283%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpsQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=3eca6ab7\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2526283/</a>"},{"pid":"fdc9b4e782ac0cb6e6b5535fc260b7be8735c9a7","tid":1795056,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"對比香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531618067fcec2ff2491189034bdd2cb7c069017","tid":1795056,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"好強既工會"},{"pid":"ce8d36dee939125249d5c588b7d8b6a82f177221","tid":1795056,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d94205ae51ae9759f8f82b4d7a6fc28aae6